<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <title>Account Termination Notice</title>
  <style>
      body {
          font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
          background-color: #f4f4f4;
          padding: 20px;
      }

      .container {
          max-width: 600px;
          margin: 0 auto;
          background-color: #ffffff;
          padding: 20px;
          border-radius: 8px;
          box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }

      h1 {
          color: #333333;
      }

      p {
          color: #666666;
          margin-bottom: 15px;
      }

      .signature {
          margin-top: 30px;
          color: #999999;
      }
      .reason {
          background-color: #ffeeba;
          padding: 10px;
          border-radius: 6px;
      }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
  <h1>Hello <%= @resource.name %>,</h1>

  <p>
    We regret to inform you that your account with CytonicMC has been terminated as
    of <%= @resource.termination_date.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %>.
    Please be advised that all data associated with your account may be permanently deleted soon after termination.
    Access to your account may be restored at a later date if deemed acceptable by a CytonicMC Administrator.
  </p>

  <p><strong>Reason for Termination:</strong></p>

  <p class="reason"><%= @resource.termination_reason %></p>

  <p>If you believe this termination notice was sent in error or if you have any questions, please contact our <a href="mailto:support@cytonic.net"> support team </a> immediately.</p>
  <p>Thank you for your understanding.</p>

  <p class="signature">Sincerely,<br>
    The CytonicMC Admin Team</p>
</div>
</body>
</html>
